name: Welcome to nharikrishnan22's homepage
tagline: A flappy bird game with a batman theme!
body:
Welcome to my Github homepage! - This site includes my Batman Wanders project!
You can play Batman Wanders on my website and try to get the best score possible! Go to the Batman Wanders project homepage at https://nharikrishnan22.github.io/webapp-flappy/ if you would like to view the full instructions or if your ready to play the game now go to https://nharikrishnan22.github.io/webapp-flappy/pages/.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
